title: J.C - A-Painter: VR Human #PaintingJam
description:
The #PaintingJam was the occasion to merge VR, Hackers and artists together. The arstist VR_Human was present with us to draw with A-Painter:  http://www.vr-human.com/

You like the idea, we invite you to read the resume of the jam:
